 ITEM 11. EXECUTIVE COMPENSATION. 

Reference is made to the 2023 Proxy Statement with respect to information about UAL's executive and director compensation and certain related matters, which is incorporated herein by reference and made a part hereof in response to the information required by Item 11 with respect to UAL. 

Information required by this item with respect to United is omitted pursuant to General Instruction I(2)(c) of Form 10-K. &#160;
